<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>創作者策略：粉絲成長與業配收益比較工具</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-a: #3498DB; /* 策略 A 藍色 */
            --primary-b: #E74C3C; /* 策略 B 紅色 */
            --bg-color: #F8F9FA;
            --card-bg: #FFFFFF;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 2fr;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .container { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
            .results-panel { grid-column: span 2; }
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .results-panel { grid-column: span 1; }
        }
        .card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        h1, h2, h3 { color: #2C3E50; margin-top: 0; }
        .strategy-title-a { color: var(--primary-a); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-a); padding-bottom: 5px; }
        .strategy-title-b { color: var(--primary-b); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-b); padding-bottom: 5px; }
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 15px; }
        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.85em;
            color: #555;
        }
        input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #dcdde1;
            border-radius: 6px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }
        button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px;
            background-color: #2C3E50;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        button:hover { background-color: #1A252F; }
        .summary-box {
            background-color: #E8F6F3;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 5px solid #1ABC9C;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 1.05em;
        }
        .chart-container {
            position: relative;
            height: 350px;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            font-size: 0.85em;
        }
        th, td {
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: right;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        th {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            text-align: center;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
        }
        .table-container {
            max-height: 350px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <h2 class="strategy-title-a">🔵 策略 A：高成長 / 均價模式</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 0.85em; color: #7f8c8d;">著重於快速累積粉絲數，以較高的接案頻率創造收入。</p>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>目前粉絲總數 (人)</label>
                <input type="number" id="fansA" value="10000">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>粉絲預估年成長率 (%)</label>
                <input type="number" id="growthA" value="30" step="1">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>每 1 萬粉的業配報價 (元)</label>
                <input type="number" id="priceA" value="1000" step="100">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>每月平均接案量 (篇/月)</label>
                <input type="number" id="postsA" value="6">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2 class="strategy-title-b">🔴 策略 B：深耕鐵粉 / 高單價模式</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 0.85em; color: #7f8c8d;">著重於內容深度與轉換率，粉絲成長較慢，但業配單價高。</p>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>目前粉絲總數 (人)</label>
                <input type="number" id="fansB" value="10000">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>粉絲預估年成長率 (%)</label>
                <input type="number" id="growthB" value="10" step="1">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>每 1 萬粉的業配報價 (元)</label>
                <input type="number" id="priceB" value="3000" step="100">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>每月平均接案量 (篇/月)</label>
                <input type="number" id="postsB" value="2">
            </div>
            
            <button onclick="calculate()">🚀 執行 10 年期收益對決</button>
        </div>

        <div class="card results-panel">
            <h2>📈 累積收益推演報告</h2>
            <div id="summary" class="summary-box">
                請點擊按鈕執行推演，查看哪一種策略在長期能創造最高收益。
            </div>
            
            <div class="chart-container">
                <canvas id="revenueChart"></canvas>
            </div>

            <h3>📅 歷年數據明細</h3>
            <div class="table-container">
                <table id="resultTable">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>年度</th>
                            <th>A 粉絲數</th>
                            <th>A 累積收益</th>
                            <th>B 粉絲數</th>
                            <th>B 累積收益</th>
                            <th>當前領先</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        let myChart = null;

        function calculate() {
            // 取得策略 A 參數
            let fA = parseFloat(document.getElementById('fansA').value);
            const gA = parseFloat(document.getElementById('growthA').value) / 100;
            const pA = parseFloat(document.getElementById('priceA').value);
            const postA = parseFloat(document.getElementById('postsA').value);

            // 取得策略 B 參數
            let fB = parseFloat(document.getElementById('fansB').value);
            const gB = parseFloat(document.getElementById('growthB').value) / 100;
            const pB = parseFloat(document.getElementById('priceB').value);
            const postB = parseFloat(document.getElementById('postsB').value);

            let cumRevA = 0;
            let cumRevB = 0;

            const years = [];
            const dataRevA = [];
            const dataRevB = [];
            let crossYear = -1;
            let initialLeader = '';

            const tbody = document.querySelector('#resultTable tbody');
            tbody.innerHTML = '';

            // 推演 10 年
            for (let year = 1; year <= 10; year++) {
                years.push(`第 ${year} 年`);

                // 計算當年度收益：(粉絲數 / 10000) * 萬粉單價 * 每月接案 * 12個月
                let yearlyRevA = (fA / 10000) * pA * postA * 12;
                let yearlyRevB = (fB / 10000) * pB * postB * 12;

                cumRevA += yearlyRevA;
                cumRevB += yearlyRevB;

                dataRevA.push(Math.round(cumRevA));
                dataRevB.push(Math.round(cumRevB));

                // 判斷領先者
                let currentLeader = cumRevA > cumRevB ? '策略 A' : '策略 B';
                if (year === 1) initialLeader = currentLeader;
                if (year > 1 && currentLeader !== initialLeader && crossYear === -1) {
                    crossYear = year; // 發生黃金交叉的年份
                }

                // 填寫表格
                const tr = document.createElement('tr');
                let status = cumRevA > cumRevB ? `<span style="color:var(--primary-a);font-weight:bold">A 勝</span>` : `<span style="color:var(--primary-b);font-weight:bold">B 勝</span>`;
                
                tr.innerHTML = `
                    <td style="text-align:center">${year}</td>
                    <td>${Math.round(fA).toLocaleString()}</td>
                    <td style="color:var(--primary-a)">$${Math.round(cumRevA).toLocaleString()}</td>
                    <td>${Math.round(fB).toLocaleString()}</td>
                    <td style="color:var(--primary-b)">$${Math.round(cumRevB).toLocaleString()}</td>
                    <td>${status}</td>
                `;
                tbody.appendChild(tr);

                // 明年粉絲成長
                fA *= (1 + gA);
                fB *= (1 + gB);
            }

            // 更新摘要報告
            const summaryDiv = document.getElementById('summary');
            let finalWinner = cumRevA > cumRevB ? '策略 A (高成長)' : '策略 B (高單價)';
            let insightText = `💡 <strong>10年推演結論：</strong> 在第 10 年時，<strong>${finalWinner}</strong> 的累積總收益較高。<br>`;
            
            if (crossYear !== -1) {
                insightText += `值得注意的是，在 <strong>第 ${crossYear} 年</strong> 發生了收益交叉！這代表短期與長期的最佳策略可能是不同的。`;
            } else {
                insightText += `在目前的設定下，${finalWinner} 從頭到尾都保持領先優勢。`;
            }
            summaryDiv.innerHTML = insightText;

            // 繪製圖表
            drawChart(years, dataRevA, dataRevB);
        }

        function drawChart(labels, dataA, dataB) {
            const ctx = document.getElementById('revenueChart').getContext('2d');
            if (myChart) myChart.destroy();

            myChart = new Chart(ctx, {
                type: 'line',
                data: {
                    labels: labels,
                    datasets: [
                        {
                            label: '策略 A 累積收益',
                            data: dataA,
                            borderColor: '#3498DB',
                            backgroundColor: 'rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.1)',
                            borderWidth: 3,
                            fill: true,
                            tension: 0.3
                        },
                        {
                            label: '策略 B 累積收益',
                            data: dataB,
                            borderColor: '#E74C3C',
                            backgroundColor: 'rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.1)',
                            borderWidth: 3,
                            fill: true,
                            tension: 0.3
                        }
                    ]
                },
                options: {
                    responsive: true,
                    maintainAspectRatio: false,
                    interaction: { mode: 'index', intersect: false },
                    plugins: {
                        tooltip: {
                            callbacks: {
                                label: function(context) {
                                    return context.dataset.label + ': $' + new Intl.NumberFormat('zh-TW').format(context.parsed.y);
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    scales: {
                        y: {
                            ticks: { callback: function(value) { return value / 10000 + ' 萬'; } }
                        }
                    }
                }
            });
        }

        window.onload = calculate;
    </script>
</body>
</html>
